title: [Firefly Villa, East Balcony]
description: Polished rails of golden linden ring the balcony and follow the length of the catwalk as it traverses the open air towards a large tree.  Bright white moonflowers trail from vines that decorate the walls of the inn and create delicate wreaths over the ebonwood and cherrywood doors.
